{"name":"Liste Druide niv 3","permission":{"default":0,"qfQAJ4nuEz9djwAx":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<h3><strong>Liste de sort de Druide niveau 3</strong></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Abjuration\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.9Oc54jfPUHQMj07q]{Dissipation de la magie}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.adB2GwSHzktgDOYo]{Protection contre les &eacute;nergies}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>&Eacute;vocation\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.XZzgZLepwTwmQGrs]{Lumi&egrave;re du jour}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.8l7Y79aTsNILt5PU]{Mur de vent}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Invocation\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.QHNBFRpqIXYm7D03]{Appel de la foudre}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.OZVOFgvaOF6CkEjH]{Invoquer des animaux}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.0ilE917g6NLkKuqT]{Temp&ecirc;te de neige}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>N&eacute;cromancie\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.wC9Ap2bgEtQVLcON]{Catalepsie}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Transmutation\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.KVqhCgoiO9fuXQqx]{Communication avec les plantes}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.z3FLlKNK0xBlc2Lw]{Croissance v&eacute;g&eacute;tale}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.90WtGczGbhwAZDUC]{Fusion dans la pierre}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.J3j8fZnbaGhwKcX0]{Marche sur l'eau}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.kNpSusSUUmpWHeyM]{Respiration aquatique}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":nu