{"name":"Liste Druide niv 5","permission":{"default":0,"qfQAJ4nuEz9djwAx":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<h3><strong>Liste de sort de Druide niveau 5</strong></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Abjuration\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.C8yaeDi60V5N67xh]{Coquille antivie}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.MpExhcEcxCLrH87D]{Entrave planaire}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.yhqi83FwjYzQYbDg]{Restauration sup&eacute;rieure}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Enchantement\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.K5tUTgzlyvyjbwGh]{Coercition mystique}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Divination\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.H3CMVcsZmbakqp2C]{Communion avec la nature}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.eoMkYpz6D0XcuqZ7]{Scrutation}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>&Eacute;vocation\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.ePo9ujJTwfxIc30x]{Mur de pierre}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.AbpUeHdRgmQyzsK1]{Soin des blessures de groupe}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Invocation\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.oE6gSp6l5nACXV0T]{Fl&eacute;au d'insectes}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.bWVBf3kDdWrEQaZ5]{Invoquer un &eacute;l&eacute;mentaire}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.BErylURWrsPQ39cE]{Passage par les arbres}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>N&eacute;cromancie\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.gFcNLd0m8zbUIbx1]{Contagion}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Transmutation\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.fQ7VHpLQPsPmPjtg]{&Eacute;veil}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.8pUO04Dfaxfb29Bf]{R&eacute;incarnation}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"widt