{"name":"Liste Clerc niv 6","permission":{"default":0,"qfQAJ4nuEz9djwAx":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<h3><strong>Liste de sort de Clerc niveau 6</strong></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Divination\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.7cYi2Q2zjmnex06B]{Trouver un chemin}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.j6LOCRMxcqbpRJWX]{Vision supr&ecirc;me}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>&Eacute;vocation\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.Imthcu5dMHcTPLfX]{Barri&egrave;re de lames Mur} @Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.NJGdaQUcg2VJTAZ2]{Barri&egrave;re de lames Sph&egrave;re}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.nCQkQJFWudOvmh2p]{Gu&eacute;rison}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Invocation\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.gjajg0rfVyJ2nQBy]{Alli&eacute; planaire}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.hjao0Wn30Rz0WUmQ]{Festin des h&eacute;ros}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.tz47AuSWArnI3Uq7]{Mot de retour}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>N&eacute;cromancie\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.ez98AHEl4JdH9FZq]{Contamination}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.AkLxKCqmjSl1jvK3]{Cr&eacute;ation de mort-vivant}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Clerc","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/green_19.jpg","effects":[],"_id":"mwIY0JBpy3FC