{"_id":"u02NAEN6pLjwrWiJ","name":"Trouver les pièges","permission":{"default":0},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Vous percevez la présence de tout piège se trouvant à portée et dans votre champ de vision. Concernant ce sort, le terme de piège désigne toute chose qui inflige soudainement ou de façon inattendue un effet considéré comme néfaste ou indésirable et que son créateur a conçu dans ce but. Ainsi, le sort prévient si une zone est affectée par une alarme, un glyphe de garde ou une fosse piégée mécanique, mais il ne révèle pas une faiblesse naturelle dans un plancher, un plafond instable ou une doline cachée.</p>\n<p>Le sort indique simplement qu'il y a un piège ; il ne précise pas où, mais vous donne une idée générale de la nature du danger qu'il représente.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des règles","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":"self","range":{"value":"36","unit":"mètres"}},"range":{"value":36,"long":null,"units":"m"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":2,"school":"div","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""},"spellType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"time":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"damageType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"concentration":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"ritual":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"prepared":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/green_14.jpg"}
{"_id":"uEYy6RPn3eaVXon5","name":"Bouclier de feu froid","permission":{"default":0,"nCN4ppSa9oQ2OVOw":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"description \">\n<p>De fines volutes de flammes enveloppent votre corps pendant toute la dur&eacute;e du sort, &eacute;mettant une lumi&egrave;re vive dans un rayon de 3 m&egrave;tres et une lumi&egrave;re faible dans un rayon additionnel de 3 m&egrave;tres. Vous pouvez mettre pr&eacute;matur&eacute;ment un terme au sort en utilisant une action.</p>\n<p>Les flammes vous offrent un bouclier chaud ou froid, comme bon vous semble. Le bouclier chaud vous apporte une r&eacute;sistance contre les d&eacute;g&acirc;ts de froid, le bouclier froid une r&eacute;sistance contre les d&eacute;g&acirc;ts de feu.</p>\n<p>De plus, quand une cr&eacute;ature situ&eacute;e dans un rayon de 1,50 m&egrave;tre autour de vous vous touche avec une attaque au corps-&agrave;-corps, le bouclier g&eacute;n&egrave;re une gerbe de flammes. Si le bouclier est chaud, il inflige 2d8 d&eacute;g&acirc;ts de feu &agrave; l'assaillant, s'il est froid, il lui inflige 2d8 d&eacute;g&acirc;ts de froid.</p>\n</div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des règles","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d8","cold"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"level":4,"school":"evo","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"Un morceau de phosphore ou une luciole","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/protect-red-3.jpg"}
{"_id":"umjT52qAQfy7iUPw","name":"Passage sans trace","permission":{"default":0},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Une aura d'ombre et de silence émane de vous et enveloppe vos compagnons, vous dissimulant aux sens d'autrui. Pendant toute la durée du sort, chaque créature que vous choisissez et qui se trouve dans un rayon de 9 mètres (vous y compris) bénéficie d'un bonus de +10 aux tests de Dextérité (Discrétion) et il devient impossible de suivre sa piste à moins de recourir à des méthodes magiques. Une créature qui profite de ce bonus ne laisse derrière elle aucune trace ni aucun autre indice de son passage.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des règles","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":9,"units":"m","type":"radius","range":{"value":"personnelle"}},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":2,"school":"abj","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":true},"materials":{"value":"Cendres d'une feuille de gui et une brindille d'épicéa","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""},"spellType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"time":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"damageType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"concentration":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"ritual":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"prepared":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/fog-air-1.jpg"}
{"_id":"uuf8OPysuWmM7aKA","name":"Cercle de mort","permission":{"default":0},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Une sphère d'énergie négative s'étend dans un rayon de 18 mètres à partir d'un point situé à portée. Chaque créature située dans la sphère doit faire un <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques#jets-de-sauvegarde\">jet de sauvegarde</a> de Constitution. Celles qui échouent subissent 8d6 dégâts nécrotiques, les autres la moitié seulement.</p>\n<p><strong>À plus haut niveau</strong>. Si vous lancez ce sort en utilisant un emplacement de niveau 7 ou supérieur, les dégâts augmentent de 2d6 par niveau au-delà du niveau 6.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des règles","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":"sphere","range":{"value":"45","unit":"mètres"}},"range":{"value":45,"long":null,"units":"m"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["8d6","necrotic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":6,"school":"nec","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"La poudre d'une perle noire broyée d'une valeur minimale de 500 po","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"level","formula":"2d6"},"spellType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"time":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"damageType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"concentration":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"ritual":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"prepared":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/air-burst-jade-3.jpg"}
{"name":"Liste Barde niv 4","permission":{"default":0,"qfQAJ4nuEz9djwAx":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<h3><strong>Liste de sort de Barde niveau 4</strong></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Abjuration\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.Bkz8upR3keOCOAwB]{Libert&eacute; de mouvement}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Enchantement\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.PTZEx74fu2m1qP68]{Compulsion}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.A0CLNbvrSJt91EK6]{Confusion}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Divination\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.7m19tw5dc8ZdhUfE]{Localiser une cr&eacute;ature}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Illusion\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.I3OmsmGd6KrtSu78]{Invisibilit&eacute; sup&eacute;rieure}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.CQ0qnTBZGBIYsQp1]{Terrain hallucinatoire}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Invocation\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.g6PEhEFxoKoangxJ]{Porte dimensionnelle}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Transmutation\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.VkcPoqLVzdtm0kxc]{M&eacute;tamorphose}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Barde","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/inventory/flute.jpg","effects":[],"_id":"vDeZljayJeiJMFUX"}
{"_id":"vGcJ91T1b2iG1FLf","name":"Choc des titans","permission":{"default":0},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Vous défiez un adversaire à portée. Tant que vous n'attaquez que cet adversaire, vous bénéficiez d'un <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques#avantage-et-désavantage\"><em>avantage</em></a> à votre première attaque à chacun de vos tours.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des règles","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":"","range":{"value":"9","unit":"mètres"}},"range":{"value":9,"long":null,"units":"m"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"enc","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""},"spellType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"time":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"damageType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"concentration":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"ritual":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"prepared":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null}},"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/yellow_17.jpg"}
{"_id":"vJG8Ky4OWYrxJ3Lg","name":"Caresse du vampire","permission":{"default":0},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Le simple contact de votre main enveloppée d'ombres peut siphonner la force vitale d'autrui pour soigner vos propres plaies. Faites une attaque de sort au corps-à-corps contre une créature située à une distance inférieure ou égale à votre allonge. Si vous touchez, elle subit 3d6 dégâts nécrotiques et vous récupérez un total de points de vie égal à la moitié des dégâts infligés. Vous pouvez dépenser votre action à chacun de vos tours pour répéter cette attaque jusqu'à la fin du sort.</p>\n<p><strong>À plus haut niveau</strong>. Si vous lancez ce sort en utilisant un emplacement de niveau 4 ou supérieur, les dégâts augmentent de 1d6 par niveau au-delà du niveau 3.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des règles","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":1,"units":"","type":"creature","range":{"value":"personnelle"}},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"","actionType":"msak","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["3d6","necrotic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":3,"school":"nec","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":true},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"level","formula":"1d6"},"spellType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"time":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"damageType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"concentration":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"ritual":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"prepared":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/violet_28.jpg"}
{"_id":"vJvC0KtYVJJm5AZM","name":"Repli expéditif","permission":{"default":0},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Ce sort vous permet de vous déplacer à une vitesse incroyable. Vous pouvez utiliser l'action <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/combattre#se-précipiter\"><em>se précipiter</em></a> quand vous le lancez, puis par une action bonus à chacun de vos tours jusqu'à ce que le sort se termine.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des règles","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":"self","range":{"value":"personnelle"}},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"trs","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":true},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""},"spellType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"time":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"damageType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"concentration":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"ritual":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"prepared":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/yellow_18.jpg"}
{"_id":"vXZM48IjWmFSVcjl","name":"Non-détection","permission":{"default":0},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Pour toute la durée du sort, vous dissimulez la cible que vous touchez aux yeux de la magie de divination. Vous pouvez prendre pour cible une créature consentante, un endroit ou un objet ne mesurant pas plus de 3 mètres dans chaque dimension. La magie de divination ne peut plus viser votre cible et les organes de scrutation magiques ne la perçoivent plus.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des règles","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":8,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":1,"units":"","type":"creature","range":{"value":"contact"}},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":3,"school":"abj","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"Une pincée de poussière de diamant d'une valeur de 25 po, que le sort consume une fois saupoudrée sur la cible","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""},"spellType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"time":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"damageType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"concentration":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"ritual":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"prepared":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/evil-eye-red-1.jpg"}
{"_id":"vYt58TXA6r9ycRbS","name":"Rayon de soleil","permission":{"default":0},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Un rayon de vive lumière jaillit de votre main sur une ligne de 18 mètres de long pour 1,50 mètre de large. Chaque créature située sur cette ligne doit effectuer un <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques#jets-de-sauvegarde\">jet de sauvegarde</a> de Constitution. Celles qui échouent subissent 6d8 dégâts radiants et sont <em>aveuglées</em> jusqu'à la fin de votre prochain tour. Les autres subissent seulement la moitié des dégâts et ne sont pas <em>aveuglées</em>. Les vases et les morts-vivants sont affectés par un <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques#avantage-et-désavantage\"><em>désavantage</em></a> lors de ce <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques#jets-de-sauvegarde\">jet de sauvegarde</a>.</p>\n<p>Vous pouvez créer une nouvelle ligne de lumière en dépensant votre action à n'importe quel tour jusqu'à la fin du sort.</p>\n<p>Pendant toute la durée du sort, une boule de lumière brille dans votre main. Elle émet une lumière vive dans un rayon de 9 mètres et une lumière faible dans un rayon de 9 mètres supplémentaires. Cette lumière est de la même nature que la lumière du soleil.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des règles","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":18,"units":"m","type":"line","range":{"value":"personnelle","unit":"(ligne"}},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["6d8","radiant"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":6,"school":"evo","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":true},"materials":{"value":"Une loupe","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""},"spellType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"time":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"damageType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"concentration":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"ritual":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"prepared":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/beam-orange-2.jpg"}
{"_id":"vbxgx39MFBNBuaTy","name":"Liste Ombrelame niv 1","permission":{"default":0,"qfQAJ4nuEz9djwAx":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<h3><strong>Liste de sort de Ombrelame niveau 1</strong></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Abjuration\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.66IkCOSiLUKg3UiL]{Alarme}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Enchantement\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.D9TLfuZWAffFIK2u]{Charme-personne}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Divination\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.pX5A4OAMYOYotCMP]{D&eacute;tection de la magie}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.a4FySK6dYuG4VtyS]{Identification}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>&Eacute;vocation\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.ko1XJNhBwiRJohtp]{Lueurs f&eacute;&eacute;riques}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Illusion\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.Isc5VZPyWaLUtuAl]{D&eacute;guisement}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.e4GUjnHspRcEhAmP]{Image silencieuse}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.ShG0UuPi9vyiViec]{Texte illusoire}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Invocation\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.s1xumIWdqUnVkiwD]{Graisse}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.DuuPeHavEjF5642F]{Nappe de brouillard}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.Tge76MEpqUQSqYid]{Poison naturel}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.TaoUfbXLU9b4da2p]{Serviteur invisible}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Transmutation\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.g8jRZr5Q44ugR8fB]{L&eacute;ger comme une plume}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.h-d-grimoire.ovCf7Oy5qS217nvD]{Saut}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type